description:
It seems there's no way to cancel your subscription as e-mails to support team remain unanswered. Thus, basically, you need to cancel your bank card to stop hiri from charging money.

The app hasn't been updated for quite a while. The issues I've discovered so far:
* scrolling is a nightmare;
* the app doesn't catch changes in network settings on Linux, specifically when my laptop moves between networks with and without proxy servers;
* interface scaling is terrible - fonts appear blurry when I scale interface to 125%.
* after I changed synchronization settings from "1 month" to "All", I can't change them back.
